item.title: Joe Brown - I'll See You In My Dreams - Key of F - Daniel Simmons
item.description: Play along video for the song I'll See You In My Dreams by Joe Brown from the channel Daniel Simmons. Chords used in the song: A7, Am, B♭, B♭6, B♭m6, B♭maj7, C, C7, Cm6, Cmaj7, D, D7, D9, Dm, E7, Edim, Em7, F, F/C, F6, F6/5, F7, Fmaj7, G7.
